{"tid":1508351,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"食相並不重要 - 陶傑","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:01:57.000Z","uid":79456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c5b5ad8bf1d171ddc5f13cf85cc4db8370448c","tid":1508351,"uid":79456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"川普在推特發出總動員令，準備與中國全面決裂。「好朋友」受到質疑，川普問「會不會是敵人」，此一昔友今敵之迅速反面，雖甚有中國特色，美國對中國威脅的焦慮，亦非做戲的假裝。<br />\n<br />\n因為對中國問題，並非僅一個GDP角度可以知道經濟真相，也不可以去中國幾次，看見城市和農村的貧富懸殊，就斷言中國很快會有社會動亂。大陸的網絡五毛言論，固然可足夠顯示中國基層人口的愚昧，但絕不表示在大學研究所實驗室裏的IT精英的智商低。<br />\n<br />\n中國只需要在十幾項「核心技術」做到精良，不一定要超過美國，也不一定要與美國並排，只要與美國接近，就已經可以傾覆西方。<br />\n<br />\n譬如中國的小型衛星「龍江二號」，可以拍攝得月球背面的圖片，而且令月球背面與地球同一直線，同框顯示。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6360be1c6cf9273fca204f002b9524e1b23bf91","tid":1508351,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"後面吹到sci-fi咁 講啲唔講啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3728c127c50c732e45d814cd441e0e604b81862d","tid":1508351,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=8e6f23de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e76f7672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\